    feat: New scroll-based homepage with WW logo
    
    - Complete homepage redesign with scroll-driven animations
    - Dark grey to light grey background transition
    - 'we build.' shrinks as you scroll with color-shifting animated dot
    - Services ticker scrolls horizontally (ai, automation, web, etc)
    - Menu floats up from bottom with serif font (Cormorant Garamond)
    - WW logo appears at end, floats and reacts to hover/click
    - Added gradient blobs and noise texture for depth
    - Multiple font families for visual variety
    - No pure black/white colors

